amily: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Booking Policy</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Hoteline reserves the right not to accept any booking or user at our sole discretion and for any cause without providing any reasons for the decline / refusal.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">In order to process your booking request, you are required to provide details of the traveller(s) according to their passport(s) and furnish us with additional information request (if any). Failure to furnish the information required will render the booking to be cancelled or void.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Your bookings are not considered confirmed until you have received a confirmation email from us. All booking requests once processed and confirmed are non-exchangeable and non-transferable and payments made are non-refundable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Member/ Agent are allowed to access to view their bookings or print the hotel vouchers at any time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Pricing</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">All prices on this site are shown in&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Malaysian Ringgit (&ldquo;RM&rdquo;)</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">, unless otherwise specifically denoted.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Prices shown on this site may vary depending on the availability of the products and/or services and subject to updates from time to time. Available prices may also include taxes and other charges.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Modification, Cancellation and Refund</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Any request for changes or cancellation shall be subject to hotel&rsquo;s terms and conditions. Some hotels may impose charges for the request and you hereby agree to pay any such charges as may be imposed by hotel.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Guaranteed booking is non-refundable and cannot be amended, revised or modified, Failure to arrive at your hotel will be treated as a No-Show and no refund will be given (hotel policy). </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Some hotels will not accept bookings made by nationals of the same country as the hotel\'s location. This is because the special rates displayed on our site, especially for some hotels in Asia, are often valid only for overseas tourists, and not for local nationals. This is a policy imposed by hotels in these countries or not by our company. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Reservation is guaranteed for arrival on the confirmed check-in date only. If you do not check-in to the hotel on the first day of your reservation and you do not alert Hoteline in advance, the remaining portion of your reservation may not receive any refund.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Disclaimer and Limitation of Liability</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Hoteline shall not be liable for any accident, damage, loss, injury, delay or irregularities whether to person or property that arise from the performance or use of this site, or from any services, products or information provided by Hoteline.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Hoteline shall not be held responsible for any direct or indirect damage derived from third party use this site, or from the incorrect use of this site.</span></p>\r\n', 'p1', 'p2', '2020-10-27 13:43:52', '2021-10-29 10:49:16'),
