(8, 'footer', 'About Us', 1, '1', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">Incorporated in 2003, Pin Sing Travel &amp; Tours (Sarawak) Sdn Bhd has grown steadily from strength to strength. The success of Pin Sing Travel over the years has been made possible through the concerted effort and hard work of our experiences, dynamic and dedicated service team. The working environment in Pin Sing Travel features with creativity and comfort to make sure that the team is able to maximize their abilities with high efficiency.&nbsp; There are five main departments in Pin Sing Travel as listed below:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">本旅行社自2003年成立以来一直秉持用心服务的理念服务顾客。团队的专业态度及资深实力备受各界好评，因而建立起好口碑。本公司也积极接洽地方会议及考察团等活动以促进旅游业的持续发展。为了提供最完善的资讯，公司各个部门提供多分类的旅游服务以符合消费族群的需求，势必为每一位顾客顷尽我们的热情与真诚的细致服务，对每一位顾客的权益负最大的责任。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableLightListAccent6\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"73\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">No.</span></span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"257\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">Main Department 主要部门</span></span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"255\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">Email address 邮址</span></span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"73\">\r\n<p class=\"