(1, 'footer', '条款和条件 ', 2, '1', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">TERMS AND CONDITIONS</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Welcome to Hoteline! Here, we are committed to make online hotel bookings a smooth and easy process hence kindly read through our terms and conditions prior to making your bookings. We reserve the right to amend, revise or modify the terms and conditions at any time at our absolute discretion without any prior notice, and such amended, revised or modified terms and conditions shall be effective upon their publication on this site.&nbsp;By making or effecting bookings via this site, you expressly agree to be bound by the terms and conditions herein.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #427dbc; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Booking Policy</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Hoteline reserves the right not to accept any booking or user at our sole discretion and for any cause without providing any reasons for the decline / refusal.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">In order to process your booking request, you are required to provide details of the traveller(s) according to their passport(s) and furnish us with additional information request (if any). Failure to furnish the information required will render the booking to be cancelled or void.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Your bookings are not considered confirmed until you have received a confirmation email from us. All booking requests once processed and confirmed are non-exchangeable and non-transferable and payments made are non-refundable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-MY;\">Member/ Age