(9, 'footer', '我们的设施', 3, '1', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">Sarawak, the land of Hornbill is a unique state with the nature beauty and always being an attractive place among tourists. As customer service is the focal point of our organization, we relentlessly search for and create new way to improve our services to clients. Pin Sing Travel welcomes guests to explore our place by providing vehicles for our inbound group and for rent as listed below:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">为了提供完善且舒适的服务，本旅行社备有多种交通设备，依不同团型的旅客给予最适合的选择。</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">另外，我们也依消费者需求提供不同种类的巴士，豪华房车与重型机车租借服务</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableLightListAccent6\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"74\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">No.</span></span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"273\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino;\">Vehicle Particulars</span></span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"74\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><sp