R</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; KUALA LUMPUR / KUCHING&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (B) </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Free until time transfer to airport. Tours End.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">We </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reserve right to amend the itinerary due to the unforeseen circumstances without</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> prior notice.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">敝社保留刪改行程內容的權力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">恕不預先通知</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'Yes', '', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, '1', NULL, '2021-11-08 11:36:41'),
(119, 2, 'photo/5514b4df73e03.jpg', 'Thailand 2', '', '', '', '5D4N Bangkok + Pattaya', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" width=\"743\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoHeader\" align=\"center\"><strong>SIGHTSEEING HIGHLIGHT&nbsp; </strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">行程简介</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"391\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ARRIVAL BANGKOK&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Upon arrival at Bangkok International Airport, meet and transfer to your hotel. Free at own leisure.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BANGKOK - PATTAYA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(B/L/D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, you will be enjoying the famous Chaophraya River Cruise continued by the Wat Arun Temple which is also known as the Temple of Dawn. After that, visit the popular Safari World &amp; Marine Theme Park in Bangkok where you will enjoy the spectacular stunt shows and wild life animal shows. Transfer to Pattaya Mimosa City of Love is certainly a great idea and will undoubtedly become a major tourist attraction. Supposedly there will be more than 300 shop and overnight. Overnight in Pattaya.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 3 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;PATTAYA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(B/L/D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, you will be taking a speed boat to Koh Laan Coral Island. You may want to try the many types of watersport activities such as water ski, parasailing, jet ski and banana boat (own expenses). In the afternoon, visit Silver Lake Grape Farm which covers 475 acres. The vineyard covers beautiful scenery, shady grape farm and relaxing atmosphere particularly sun set scenic view. Continue to Laser Buddha. A very interesting area of well kept gardens with the largest laser etched Buddha image in the world and is inlayed with gold leaf. It is 130m high and was done in 1996 to commemorate the 50th anniversary of the King.&nbsp; Process to Pattaya Floating Market. Overnight in Pattaya.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 4 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;PATTAYA &ndash; BANGKOK&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(B/L/D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, visit Pattaya Sheep Farm by Chang Siam is the newest tourist attraction here in Pattaya, it opened its doors on the 8th of june 2013. This is a great place, especially for children. After lunch, Transfer to Bangkok, continue to Four Faced Buddha, the Faces represents the Face of Peace and Health, Face of Good Fortune, Face of Good Relationships and Face of Protection against Evils. Process to Siam Paragon or MBK Shopping Complex. Overnight in Bangkok.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 5 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;DEPARTURE FROM BANGKOK&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(B)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, free at own leisure till transfer to airport for departure.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Shopping Stop: Gems &amp; Leather Factory , Honey , Local Product ( Subject to change )</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"352\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第一天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">抵达曼谷</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK5231 KCH/KUL 0700-0840</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK882 KUL/DMK 1130-1250</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">到达曼谷国际机场后，由专业导游迎接转乘空调旅遊巴士送回酒店。</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自由活动。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第二天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">曼谷</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">芭提雅</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后，您将欣赏著名的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Chaophraya River Cruise </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">及参观郑皇寺也被称为黎明寺。接下来，您将到曼谷观赏知名度最高的野生动物园与海洋主题公园，</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在这之后您可以欣赏壮观的特技表演和野生动物表演。续往游览米默莎爱情小镇</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">富有法式风格之建筑，商店有当地特色工艺品、服饰及有各种美食餐厅在内。在芭提雅住宿一晚。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第三天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">芭提雅</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后，您将乘坐快艇到珊瑚岛。您可以在这里尝试到水上活动如滑水，滑翔伞，水上摩托艇香蕉船（自费）等多种类型。下午，前往参观银湖葡萄园</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">这农场占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 475</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英亩，在那阴凉的农场感觉格外轻松，日落的景色更是特别。</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">接着前往</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">七珍佛山，约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">130</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">米高，建于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1996</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以纪念国王</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年，是世界上最大的蚀刻的佛图像并镶嵌金箔。驱车前往参观由泰国观光局规划了将近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年，集合了泰国北部、东北部、中部及南部各地方特色名产的水上市集，称为</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">席攀水上市场。在芭提雅住宿一晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第四天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">芭提雅</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> &ndash; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">曼谷</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后，前往充满村野色彩的芭提雅牧羊农庄感受美如画的田园之美，一大片绿色盈盈的草原，大群白绵羊可爱的食相，仿佛沉浸在童话故事的场景。继续参观四面佛，一面代表着和平和健康，一面是好运，一面良好姻缘，一面防止病魔。之后前往暹羅百麗宮或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MBK</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">購物廣場自由大肆公务至指定集合时间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在曼谷住宿一晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第五天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">启程回国</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">FD313 DMK/KUL 1200-1505</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK5226 KUL/KCH 1735-1920</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后</span><