(118, 2, 'photo/5514b94e85797.jpg', 'Thailand 1', '', '', '', '4D3N Bangkok + Pattaya ', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" width=\"737\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoHeader\" align=\"center\"><strong>SIGHTSEEING HIGHLIGHT&nbsp; </strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">行程简介</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"391\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ARRIVAL BANGKOK&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Upon arrival at Bangkok International Airport, you will be met by our representatives and will be transferred to your hotel. Overnight in Bangkok.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BANGKOK - PATTAYA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(B/L/D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, you will be enjoying the famous <strong>Chaophraya River Cruise</strong> continued by the <strong>Wat Arun Temple</strong> which is also known as the Temple of Dawn. After that, visit the popular <strong>Safari World &amp; Marine Theme</strong> <strong>Park</strong> in Bangkok where you will enjoy the spectacular stunt shows and wild life animal shows. Transfer to Pattaya </span><strong>Mimosa</strong><strong> City of Love</strong> is certainly a great idea and will undoubtedly become a major tourist attraction. Supposedly there will be more than 300 shop<span lang=\"EN-US\">. Overnight in Pattaya.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong>Day </strong><strong>3</strong><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>&nbsp;PATTAYA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>(B/L/D)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\">After breakfast, you will be taking a speed boat to <strong>Koh Laan Coral Island</strong>. You may want to try the many types of watersport activities such as water ski, parasailing, jet ski and banana boat (own expenses).&nbsp; Next to <strong>Pattaya Sheep Farm</strong> by Chang Siam is the newest tourist attraction here in Pattaya, it opened its doors on the 8th of june 2013. This is a great place, especially for children. In the afternoon, visit <strong>Silver Lake Grape Farm</strong> which covers 475 acres. The vineyard covers beautiful scenery, shady grape farm and relaxing atmosphere particularly sun set scenic view. Continue to <strong>Laser Buddha.</strong> A very interesting area of well kept gardens with the largest laser etched Buddha image in the world and is inlayed with gold leaf. It is 130m high and was done in 1996 to commemorate the 50th anniversary of the King. Process to <strong>Pattaya Floating Market</strong>. Overnight in Pattaya.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong>Day </strong><strong>4</strong><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>&nbsp;PATTAYA &ndash; BANGKOK AIRPORT</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(B)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\">After breakfast, free at own leisure till transfer to airport for departure with a sweet memories.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong>Note: Flight must depart from Bangkok after 1400pm, flight before 1400pm extra charge will be apply</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong>Shopping Stop: Gems &amp; Leather Factory , Honey , Local Product&nbsp; (Subject to change)</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"346\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第一天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">抵达曼谷</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">到达曼谷国际机场后，由专业导游迎接转乘空调旅遊巴士送回住宿酒店。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第二天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">曼谷</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">芭提雅</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后，您将欣赏著名的</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Chaophraya River Cruise</span></strong> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">及参观<strong>郑皇寺</strong>也被称为黎明寺。接下来，您将到曼谷观赏知名度最高的<strong>野生动物园与海洋主题公园</strong>，</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在这之后您可以欣赏壮观的特技表演和野生动物表演。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">续往游览</span><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">米默莎爱情小</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">镇</span></strong> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">富有法式风格之建筑，商店有当地特色工艺品、服饰及有各种美食餐厅在内。在芭提雅住宿一晚。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第三天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">芭提雅</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后，您将乘坐快艇到<strong>珊瑚岛</strong>。您可以在这里尝试到水上活动如滑水，滑翔伞，水上摩托艇香蕉船（自费）等多种类型。</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">下午</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">前往参观充满村野色彩的<strong>芭提雅牧羊农庄</strong>感受美如画的田园之美，一大片绿色盈盈的草原，大群白绵羊可爱的食相，仿佛沉浸在童话故事的场景。下午，前往参观<strong>银湖葡萄园</strong></span><strong>,</strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">这农场占</span> 475<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英亩，在那阴凉的农场感觉格外轻松，日落的景色更是特别。 接着前往 <strong>七珍佛山，</strong>约</span>130<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">米高，建于</span>1996<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以纪念国王</span>50<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年，是世界上最大的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">蚀刻的佛图像并镶嵌金箔。驱车前往参观由泰国观光局规划了将近</span>2<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年，集合了泰国北部、东北部、中部及南部各地方特色名产的水上市集，称为<strong>席攀水上市场</strong>。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">第</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">天</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong> <strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">启程回国</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>(</strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">早</span></strong><strong>)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">早餐</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">后</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自由活动至</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">送往</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">机场启程回国</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">结</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">束</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">天愉快旅程</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">注意：航班时间必须在</span></strong><strong>1400</strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">后离开曼谷</span></strong><strong>, </strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">如航班时间早于</span></strong><strong>1400</strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">将会有额外的收费</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">购物站</span></strong> <strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：宝石</span></strong><strong>&amp; </strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">皮革</span></strong> <strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，蜂蜜</span></strong> <strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，土特产</span></strong> <span lang=\"EN-GB\">( </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">保留更改的权利</span> <span lang=\"EN-AU\">)</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">We </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reserve right to amend the itinerary due to the unforeseen circumstances without</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> prior notice.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">敝社保留刪改行程內容的權力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">恕不預先通知</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'Yes', '', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, '1', NULL, '2021-11-08 11:36:55'),
(121, 2, 'photo/5514b5056db3e.jpg', 'Thailand 4', '', '', '', '4D3N Phuket ', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"center\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">DAYS 3 NIGHTS RELAXING PHUKET </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">普吉岛</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 739px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"385\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">PACKAGE INCLUDED</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"354\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">PACKAGE EXCLUDES</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"385\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&uuml;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Meet and greet by local representative</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&uuml;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Air ticket </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&uuml;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">All meals as per itinerary (non halal or vegetarian)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&uuml;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Escorted orientation tour by Mandarin speaking guide + tipping</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&uuml;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">All entrance fees as per itinerary</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"354\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ucirc;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">All personal expenses &amp; porterage</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ucirc;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Entry visa application (if applicable)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ucirc;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Travel insurance coverage</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ucirc;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">High season surcharge (if applicable)</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" width=\"739\">\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 738px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" width=\"738\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">SIGHTSEEING TOUR </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">行程简介</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"383\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 1&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ARRIVAL PHUKET &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Upon arrival at Phuket International Airport, meet up our representative and proceed to hotel check-in. Dinner will be served at local restaurant</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; PHI PHI ISLAND TOUR BY CRUISE&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (B/L/D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">0730 pickup from hotel. Sightseeing around Phi Phi Lay Islands. (Maya Bay, Loh Samah Bay, Pileh Cove &amp; pass by Viking Cave) Swimming &amp; snorkelling at Monkey Beach or Maya Bay. Great lunch at Phi Phi Don. You get the free time To explore the surroundings and relaxing on the beach.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> PHUKET DICOVERY TOUR&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">(B/L/D)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, proceed to Phuket City Tour. You will be brought to visit the <strong>Chino-Portugese Style Buildings</strong> followed by visiting the <strong>Saphan Hin Park</strong>, <strong>Cashew Nut factory</strong>, <strong>Gems Factory</strong>, <strong>Bridnest Shop</strong>,</span> <strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Chalong Temple</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">, <strong>Sea Gypsy Village</strong>, <strong>Rawai Beach</strong>, <strong>Prompthep Cape</strong> where you can view its stunning beauty.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;PHUKET-KUALA LUMPUR&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">(B)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, free at own leisure till</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">transfer to airport</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"354\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第一天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">抵达普吉岛</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK5203 KCH/KUL 0920-1100</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK824 KUL/HKT 1240-1300</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">抵达机场后，被送往酒店。晚餐将在当地餐厅。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第二天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">披披岛</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&