 lang=\"EN-US\">Prompthep</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">海角在那您能观看到那秀丽壮观的全景。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">第</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">天</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong> <strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">启程回国</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK825 HKT/KUL 1335-1600</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK5234 KUL/KCH 1820-2010</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">早餐</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自由活动至</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">送往</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">机场启程回国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">结</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">束</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">天愉快旅程。</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">We </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reserve right to amend the itinerary due to the unforeseen circumstances without</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> prior notice.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">敝社保留刪改行程內容的權力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">恕不預先通知</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'Yes', '', 0, '', '', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, '1', NULL, '2021-11-08 11:37:00'),
(122, 8, 'photo/5514b5192b589.jpg', 'Vietnam 1', '', '', '', '5D4N Hanoi + Halong Bay', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><strong>5D4N HANOI + HALONG BAY</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 1:&nbsp; KUCHING / KUALA LUMPUR </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">古晋</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> / </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">吉隆坡</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK5227 KCH/KUL 1945-2125 (subject to change)&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Overnight at KLIA2 hotel. </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">飞往吉隆坡。夜宿机场酒店。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Day 2:&nbsp; KUALA LUMPUR / HANOI&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (MOB, L, D)&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">AK516 KUL/HAN 0630-0850</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Upon arrival at Noi Bai International Airport, meet and transfer to Hanoi downtown to visit the <strong>West Lake</strong> with <strong>Tran Quoc Temple</strong>, <strong>Hoan Kiem Lake</strong> and shopping at <strong>36 Old Quarter,</strong> enjoy<strong> Water Puppet Show</strong>. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">吉隆坡</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> / </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">河内</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">抵达河内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">内牌国际机场后由专业导游接待前往河内参观【西湖】及【镇国寺】。乘车到河内市中心观光市内著名的【还剑湖】，逛【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">36</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">古式街道】购物，欣赏越南著名的的【水上木偶戏表演】。晚餐於当地餐厅。</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">DAY 3: HANOI &ndash; HALONG &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (B/L/D)</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />Breakfast at hotel, visit <strong>Ho Chi Minh Mausoleum</strong>, <strong>Ho Chi Minh Palace, Ba Dinh Square, Uncle Ho\' Still House</strong>, <strong>One Pillar Pagoda</strong> after that visit <strong>Temple of Literature.</strong> After lunch, transfer to Halong Bay, dinner and overnight in Halong Bay.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">河内</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> -</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">下龙湾</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（早</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">午</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晚）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">早餐后，参观<strong>【</strong>胡志明主席陵墓】，<strong>【</strong>主席府】，<strong>【</strong></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴亭广场</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">】，<strong>【</strong>胡志明主席故居】，【一柱庙】。接着，参观【文庙】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">越南首间大学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。午餐后，前往广宁省的下龙湾（一九九四年已获得联合国科教文公认为世界天然之遗产</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，也刚刚成为新世界七大自然遗产之一</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，是越南著名岛屿风景区）。晚餐於当地餐厅。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">DAY 4: HALONG &ndash; HANOI &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (B/L/D)<br /></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">After breakfast, transfer to Halong Boat station to take our private boat to visit the world Heritage Halong Bay about 4 hours , our boat will bring us to visit <strong>Paradise Grotto</strong>, <strong>Kissing Chicken Rock, Fisherman Village</strong>, lunch will be served on boat with fresh Halong Seafood, enjoy <strong>Vietnamese Traditional Coffee.</strong> Back to Hanoi, visit <strong>French Opera House.</strong> Dinner at local restaurant, overnight in Hanoi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">下龙湾</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> - </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">河内</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs